    <item>
      <title>财政部官员称南非可能于 2025 年 10 月退出黑钱名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/south-africa-may-exit-dirty-money-list-by-october-2025-treasury-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部官员伊斯梅尔·莫莫尼亚特 (Ismail Momoniat) 表示，如果没有意外，南非应该在明年 6 月或 10 月之前解决打击非法资金流动方面存在的突出问题，以便退出全球黑钱名单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/south-africa-may-exit-dirty-money-list-by-october-2025-treasury-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 18:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列向哈马斯领导人提供安全撤离加沙地带的途径以结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/israel-offers-hamas-leader-safe-exit-from-gaza-in-bid-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级官员称，以色列提议给予哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔安全离开加沙的通道，作为交换，哈马斯必须释放人质并放弃对加沙地带的控制，尽管双方能否达成停火协议的疑虑日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/israel-offers-hamas-leader-safe-exit-from-gaza-in-bid-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 18:11:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治风险加剧，海上风电支持者支持哈里斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/offshore-wind-proponents-back-harris-as-political-risk-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一晚上，海上风电支持者聚集在曼哈顿，为民主党总统候选人卡马拉·哈里斯提供支持和资金，凸显了人们对美国新兴产业面临的选举风险日益增长的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/offshore-wind-proponents-back-harris-as-political-risk-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 18:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西企业敦促卢拉就补缴税款达成更好的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brazilian-companies-pushing-lula-for-better-deals-on-back-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦计划通过解决企业税务纠纷来平衡预算，但由于一些巴西大型企业坚持要求获得更好的待遇，这一计划面临障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/brazilian-companies-pushing-lula-for-better-deals-on-back-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:55:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯在关键辩论中取得转折性胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/presidential-debate-trump-harris-reach-for-game-changing-moment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯参加周二的辩论是为了同一个目标——这一时刻将有助于他们在民意调查结果基本持平的竞选中取得优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/presidential-debate-trump-harris-reach-for-game-changing-moment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
